[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written evidence from [bold]the [bold]London Assembly Transport Committee[bold] [bold](CYS0050)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]I am writing, on behalf of the London Assembly Transport Committee, to 
[normal]provide
